attributes.Long form description: The student is to disassemble the side table. The student starts to unscrew the legs of the side table using the allen wrench. Next, the student disassembles the legs and trays by detaching them from the hex socket head. Lastly, the student puts them all on the table neatly.

attributes.Transcription: We will now disassemble the IKEA side table KNARREVIK, so please go ahead and disassemble it.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the first leg of the furniture.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should not drop hex_socket_head.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the second leg of the furniture.
The student disassembles the top tray of the furniture.
The student disassembles the third leg of the furniture.
The student disassembles the fourth leg of the furniture.

attributes.Transcription: Okay, you can now press stop.
